
---

**StreamMirrorLine**  
**Description:**  
Displays live data with a central baseline and mirrored fluctuation lines to emphasize directional changes.

```markdown
# StreamMirrorLine - Bidirectional Metric Visualizer

StreamMirrorLine renders live numeric streams on a mirror axis to highlight upward/downward velocity and symmetry.

## Features
- Mirror-axis scrollable chart  
- Live rendering  
- Matplotlib backend

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamMirrorLine.git
cd StreamMirrorLine
python visualize.py
